'''''Battle of the Atlantic: The Ocean Lifeline''''' is a 1984 video game published by [[Simulations Canada]].

==Gameplay==
''Battle of the Atlantic'' is a game in which the [[Battle of the Atlantic]] is simulated.<ref name="CGW29"/>

==Reception==
William H. Harrington reviewed the game for ''[[Computer Gaming World]]'', and stated that "a sophisticated and highly playable simulation of this decisive World War II naval conflict."<ref name="CGW29">{{cite magazine |last=Harrington |first=William H. |title=Battle of the Atlantic |magazine=Computer Gaming World |date=June–July 1986 |volume=1 |issue=29 |pages=22–23}}</ref>

